thread.title: Ethics Panel Defers Probe Into GOPer's Finances, Signals DOJ Looking Into It
thread.title_full: Ethics Panel Defers Probe Into GOPer's Finances, Signals DOJ Looking Into It

author: Esme Cribb
title: Ethics Panel Defers Probe Into GOPer's Finances, Signals DOJ Looking Into It
text:
The House Ethics Committee announced Thursday that it is deferring its investigation into Rep. Duncan Hunter (R-CA), signaling that the Department of Justice may be conducting its own probe into alleged campaign finance violations.
